#, fuzzy
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When you run a Quarkus application in dev mode, you can expose a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server.\n"
"It presents the methods used by the DevUI *MCP tools* (methods you can call) and the data exposed by *MCP resources*."
msgstr "在开发模式下运行 Quarkus 应用程序时，可以公开模型上下文协议（MCP）服务器。它展示了 DevUI *MCP 工具* 使用的方法（你可以调用的方法）和 *MCP 资源* 公开的数据。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Connecting a coding agent (Recommended)"
msgstr "连接编码代理（推荐）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The **recommended** way to connect an AI coding agent to your Quarkus application is through the https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-agent-mcp[Quarkus Agent MCP] server.\n"
"This standalone MCP server provides a complete development experience and is the preferred integration method for all AI coding agents."
msgstr "将人工智能编码代理连接到 Quarkus 应用程序的 *推荐* 方法是通过 link:https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus-agent-mcp[Quarkus Agent MCP] 服务器。这种独立的 MCP 服务器可提供完整的开发体验，是所有人工智能编码代理的首选集成方法。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Quarkus Agent MCP server offers significant advantages over direct connection:"
msgstr "与直接连接相比，Quarkus Agent MCP 服务器具有显著优势："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Project scaffolding** — Create new Quarkus applications with customizable extensions"
msgstr "*项目脚手架* --利用可定制的扩展功能创建新的 Quarkus 应用程序"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Application lifecycle management** — Start, stop, and restart your application, with automatic recovery from crashes"
msgstr "*应用程序生命周期管理* --启动、停止和重启应用程序，并从崩溃中自动恢复"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Dev MCP proxy** — Access all Dev MCP tools from the running application"
msgstr "*Dev MCP 代理* - 从运行中的应用程序访问所有 Dev MCP 工具"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Documentation search** — Semantic search across Quarkus documentation using embeddings"
msgstr "*文档搜索* - 利用嵌入式技术在 Quarkus 文档中进行语义搜索"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Extension skills** — Get extension-specific coding patterns, best practices, and testing guidelines"
msgstr "*扩展技能* - 获取特定于扩展的编码模式、最佳实践和测试指南"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/dev-mcp.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Version management** — Check for updates and get upgrade reports"
msgstr "*版本管理* - 检查更新并获取升级报告"

